// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1539 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 6a152713-40eb-5faf-b65f-b0d0b90364eb

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
